name: Crypto Bolivar #001 Josefa Camejo by Eva Cortez
description:
Josefa Camejo in the Metaverse.

Interpretation of the original banknote, showing one of the heroines of the independence of my country Venezuela.

Special edition in the framework of a new monetary reconversion in my country. 

This collection invites us to reflect on the value of fiat money, devaluation and cryptocurrencies as an alternative to safeguard the value of our artistic work.

Digital animation on offer.
Animation resolution 1500px x 3405px in GIF format.
Date of realization: August 08, 2021.
Technique: Digital drawing and 2D animation.
Software: Medibang Pain Pro.

The Artwork may not be reproduced commercially.
The author reserves the right to use the image of the artwork for merchandising.


Thank you for supporting my work!
